{
  "stem": "23278.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then there was a law that all those refugees could not live so near the border.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had to live at least 200 miles inland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's how they ended up in Dijon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know how many there were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were maybe a dozen here, a dozen there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they were speaking German, and they were very much there, having their coffee klatch and their pastries, not in the French manner.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, because they were old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, they're people the age of my mother, and I didn't go to cafe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I suppose some had.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- the Tradelius did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, they had Annalise.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also at that time, something that has bothered me since.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had those big cafe houses that were quite elegant, where women met for tea.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was not a place for drinking, but it was a nice place to meet, like in Paris now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had orchestras.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And those orchestras at the time were made up, I realized later, from those Jewish refugees.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe lawyers, doctors, people like that who were of excellent education, who were amateur, probably, playing the violin, the piano, and put together orchestra to survive.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because what they knew, whether in medicine or law, you couldn't use in France.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
